text: Pseudophallus elcapitanensis is a species of marine fish belonging to the family Syngnathidae. They can be found within freshwater rivers and streams in Central America from Jimenez, Costa Rica to Rio Chico, Panama. == References == == External links == * Pseudophallus elcapitanensis at FishBase Category:Syngnathidae Category:Fish described in 1914
title: Pseudophallus elcapitanensis
